	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers#Mask_.28.242001.29_.3E_write">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_ ... _.3E_write</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />The line states that writing #$30 to $2001 will produce a monochrome display. It seems that is incorrect. Writing #$1F will produce the monochrome display. Writing #$30 will only remove the background rendering and intensify red.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
